# pi-notes knowledge graph

The human navigation index is programmatic.

Open the rendered Brain index at:

```text
/notes
```

The Document Host discovers `.brain/**/*.svx`, sorts entries into PARA sections, and links each entry route automatically.

## Rule

Do not maintain a manual list of Brain pages here. Manual page lists rot immediately.

Use this file only as the root marker for `brain:check` and as a short explanation of how the index works.
